Title: mk_logwatch: no longer resolve symlinks
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1593610102
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

Symbolic links of logfiles no longer get resolved to the actual path.
Some log file paths might change on a daily basis, so resolving symlink paths could result in missing files for the software.
This will now be avoided by this fix.
